* [/] %? :project:
:PROPERTIES:
:ID:       %(org-id-uuid)
:CREATED:  %U
:COOKIE_DATA: todo recursive
:END:

#+BEGIN: gantt :tstart "<today>" :tend "<+3m>" :tunit "month"
#+END:

- [ ] *Capture* current thoughts on the project.

- [ ] *Review* folders (or tags) that might contain relevant notes.

- [ ] *Search* for related terms across all folders.

- [ ] *Move* (or tag) relevant notes to the project folder.

- [ ] *Create* an outline of the collected notes and plan the project.
